<item>
            <title>[LU-9167] lctl mdt.*.hsm_control=purge uses the CDT&apos;s env</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9167</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;hsm_cancel_all_actions()&lt;/tt&gt; assumes that we are running in the CDT&apos;s context but we are really running in the context of some user process (usually lctl). Therefore &lt;tt&gt;hsm_cancel_all_actions()&lt;/tt&gt; must not use the CDT environment (via &lt;tt&gt;mdt-&amp;gt;mdt_coordinator.cdt_env&lt;/tt&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
